Security & Encription

- Encription:
  - In Transit:
    - SSL/TLS
  - At Rest:
    - Server Side Encription
      - S3 Managed Keys - SSE-S3
      - AWS Keys Management Service, Managed Keys - SSE-KMS
      - Server Side Encription With Customer Provided Keys - SSE-Control
    - Client Side Encription

- Security:
  - by default all newly bucket are PRIVATE
  - Setup access control using:
    - Bucket Policies
    - Access Control List
  - S3 can be configured to create access logs, to logs all requests made to them. This can be done to another bucket


